  "description": "Most granola recipes are using a combination of nuts and dried fruits, but our favorite is the simplest of all: with just dried cranberries.\n\nCombined with yogurt and fresh berries, makes an awesome breakfast.\n\nThis _was_ our favorite granola recipe until we became date addicts and invented [date granola](https://tacohuaco.co/recipes/date-granola/), and later the [Morning crunch granola](https://tacohuaco.co/recipes/morning-crunch-granola/).",
